hopobject.body: We used to work together pharmacyworld.wixsite.com The scandal, which was known among Keenan's small firm peers, did not deter 489 small firms from supporting his candidacy in a three-way race earlier this month. The alleged link between Keenan's firm and Shoffner's legal problems was not an issue until it was reported last week by Investment News, small firm executives told Reuters. That piece led to some speculation that FINRA should do more to check out board candidates.
